Resource Profile: Composition - Jurisdiction Live Birth Report

Official URL: http://hl7.org/fhir/us/bfdr/StructureDefinition/Composition-jurisdiction-live-birth-report Version: 2.0.0-Ballot
Draft as of 2024-05-01 Computable Name: CompositionJurisdictionLiveBirthReport

This Composition profile contains information of a live birth and the issuance of a Birth Certificate to be recorded and communicated to the national statistics agency.

The data requirements for jurisdictional reporting of live births are based on the Edit Specifications for the 2003 Revision of the U.S. Standard Certificate of Birth.

For information on IJE and Forms Mappings, see the CompositionProviderLiveBirthReport page.

Usage:

  • Use this Resource Profile: Bundle - Document Birth Report
  • Examples for this Resource Profile: Composition/composition-jurisdiction-live-birth-babyg-quinn
